# This is a plain static site (HTML/CSS/JS/data) with no build step.
# node_modules should never exist here, but this exists as a safeguard --
# a stray package.json (like the one just removed) makes Cloudflare Pages
# treat this as a Node.js project needing `npm install`, which pulls in
# Cloudflare's own wrangler/workerd tooling (a 121MB+ binary) and then
# deploys the entire node_modules tree as static assets, exceeding the
# 25MB per-asset limit and failing the build.
node_modules/
package-lock.json
